window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b><i>One night. Six stories. Total nuclear annihilation.</i></b></p> <p><b>THE BRUTES</b></p> <p>Tonight was meant to be about kink. Our lives are a nightmare of last-minute deployments and near misses, and we needed the break.</p> <p>Instead, <i>we</i> broke. The whole world broke.</p> <p>But as city after city is blown apart, and with a club full of civilians to protect, we have to pull it together and get them to safety. No matter how we’re feeling. No matter how many family members are disintegrating into ash. We have a job to do, so we’ll be each other’s strength.</p> <p>Even if it means walking into bomb-fire together.</p> <p><b>EDEN</b></p> <p>I’m alone.</p> <p>Please, someone forgive me for what I have to do.</p> <p>I don’t think I can.</p>"; 
